---
import DocsLayout from '../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro';
---

<DocsLayout title="Moat Documentation" description="Run agents in containers with credential injection and full observability">
  <div class="max-w-3xl">
    <h1 class="font-serif text-5xl font-normal leading-tight tracking-tight mb-6 mt-12">
      Let agents break things <span class="text-sky-700 italic">safely</span>
    </h1>

    <p class="text-xl text-stone-600 mb-12 leading-relaxed">
      Moat runs AI agents in isolated containers with credential injection and observability.
    </p>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-12">
      <div class="border-l-2 border-sky-700 pl-4">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-normal mb-3">Container Isolation</h2>
        <p class="text-stone-600">
          Code runs in Docker or Apple containers, separate from your host system.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="border-l-2 border-sky-700 pl-4">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-normal mb-3">Credential Injection</h2>
        <p class="text-stone-600">
          OAuth tokens and API keys injected at the network layer—never in environment variables.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="border-l-2 border-sky-700 pl-4">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-normal mb-3">Full Observability</h2>
        <p class="text-stone-600">
          Every run captures container logs, HTTP traces, and a tamper-proof audit log.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="border-l-2 border-sky-700 pl-4">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-normal mb-3">Declarative Config</h2>
        <p class="text-stone-600">
          Define runtime, credentials, and policies in a simple <code class="bg-stone-200 px-1">agent.yaml</code> file.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-stone-800 text-stone-100 px-6 py-4 font-mono text-sm mb-12 overflow-x-auto">
      <div class="text-stone-400"># Install</div>
      <div class="mb-3">$ go install github.com/andybons/moat/cmd/moat@latest</div>

      <div class="text-stone-400"># Grant access to GitHub</div>
      <div class="mb-3">$ moat grant github</div>

      <div class="text-stone-400"># Run an agent with credentials</div>
      <div>$ moat run --grant github -- curl https://api.github.com/user</div>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-4">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-normal mb-6">Get Started</h2>

      <a href="/moat/getting-started/introduction"
         class="block border border-stone-300 hover:border-sky-700 hover:bg-stone-50 p-4 transition-colors group">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-stone-800 group-hover:text-sky-700 mb-1">Introduction</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-stone-600">Learn about Moat's core concepts and architecture</p>
          </div>
          <span class="text-stone-400 group-hover:text-sky-700">→</span>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a href="/moat/getting-started/installation"
         class="block border border-stone-300 hover:border-sky-700 hover:bg-stone-50 p-4 transition-colors group">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-stone-800 group-hover:text-sky-700 mb-1">Installation</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-stone-600">Platform-specific installation instructions</p>
          </div>
          <span class="text-stone-400 group-hover:text-sky-700">→</span>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a href="/moat/getting-started/quick-start"
         class="block border border-stone-300 hover:border-sky-700 hover:bg-stone-50 p-4 transition-colors group">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-stone-800 group-hover:text-sky-700 mb-1">Quick Start</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-stone-600">Guided walkthrough of your first Moat run</p>
          </div>
          <span class="text-stone-400 group-hover:text-sky-700">→</span>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-stone-300">
      <p class="text-sm text-stone-600">
        Moat is open source and in active development. APIs and configuration formats may change.
        View the{' '}
        <a href="https://github.com/majorcontext/moat" class="text-sky-700 hover:text-sky-800 underline">
          GitHub repository
        </a>
        {' '}for the latest updates.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</DocsLayout>
